yeti.monitoring
Class YetiMonitoringLogProcessor

java.lang.Object
  yeti.YetiLogProcessor
      yeti.monitoring.YetiMonitoringLogProcessor
Direct Known Subclasses:
YetiGUIFaultsOverTime, YetiGUINumberOfCallsOverTime, YetiGUINumberOfFailuresOverTime, YetiGUINumberOfVariablesOverTime
public abstract class YetiMonitoringLogProcessor
extends YetiLogProcessor

Class that represents a composable log processor. Basically this class implements the proxy pattern for log processors. It is used in the GUI for combining the several inspectors on the GUI.

Author:
Manuel Oriol (manuel@cs.york.ac.uk)
